115/118/120 snatches from the local meet we did last weekend. It’s definitely exciting to hit numbers like this when we aren’t peaking.  118 and 120 were both meet PR’s.

I’m still getting used to not hitting snatches. I hated them for like 3 years. They actually are kind of fun when you do them right!

