Look good feel good didn’t quite work the other day 🤣😭 
@lululemon it’s rulu ribbed cropped half zip - I love this layering piece & wore it in my last half. Rulu material is warm, soft & great for colder months. Reflective details at the cuff, hand pockets (cuff flips over to mittens,) and a zippered front pocket. I should have went with my normal size rather than sizing up.
Bicondo Amazon tank, dupe of fp movement. Thick and cute! 
@lululemon wunder train strappy bra 
@lululemon Align shorts in Vitapink. double lined.
@saucony Endorphin speed 5- Ive only worn them a handful of times but I truly think my calves and shins are going to end up injured if I continue wearing these shoes. Crazy pain and knots throughout my calves from a lower drop than I’m used to & even though they’re so cute they are not working for me at all 💔 
@lululemon fast and free running belt 
@feetures socks- ultra lite always 

